review_text:
A pleasant surprise from WWE Studios. NO ONE LIVES is a tight, nasty genre gem from Japanese schlockmeister Ryuhei Kitamura.

Also features suitably gritty cinematography (on Super16mm film) from TEXAS CHAINSAW MASSACRE's Daniel Pearl.
